FBIS4-61768 "drsov090_s_94007" FBIS-SOV-94-090 Daily Report 9 May 1994 Georgia Radioactive Equipment Stolen From Tbilisi Institute Radioactive Equipment Stolen From Tbilisi Institute LD0905211894 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel Network in Russian 2000 GMT 9 May 94 LD0905211894 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel Network Russian BFN [Text] A radioactive machine, previously used to help eliminate the effects of the Chernobyl disaster and contained in a special box on the premises of the radiological institute in a Tbilisi suburb, has been stolen by unknown persons. According to the institute, the polluted machine is extremely dangerous to people around it. There has been no trace of the thieves so far.
